FatPtr General Case (3 pointers + i32 = 224 bits):
+----------+----------+----------+----------+
| VTable*  | Data*    | Region*  | i32      |
| (64b)    | (64b)    | (64b)    | (32b)    |
+----------+----------+----------+----------+

FatPtr Inline Case (1 pointer + 128b data + i32 = 224 bits):
+----------+---------------------+----------+
| VTable*  | 128-bit Data        | i32      |
| (64b)    | (128b)              | (32b)    |
+----------+---------------------+----------+